{"tid":588933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇現代化詠春/中國功夫","createTime":"2018-03-11T14:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T11:32:38.000Z","uid":71568,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"681b9f910c548b6450e411cd73fb20ac06aba441","tid":588933,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/222145_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F222145_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=feb952c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李小龍係半個世紀前創出截拳道，提倡武者<br />\n<br />\n應該放棄門派界限，學習各家之長。但係到<br />\n<br />\n上年我地都仲有太極老宗師比mma佬打到<br />\n<br />\n變豬頭咁。似乎中國武術既現代化少之又<br />\n<br />\n少，同柔道摔跤泰拳呢d差好遠。但係又唔<br />\n<br />\n係話中國武術完全冇用wor(虎爪醉拳果d另<br />\n<br />\n計)，例如我google過外國討論mma既時候<br />\n<br />\n講到詠春，屌既都係話訓練方法on9, 但係<br />\n<br />\n話&quot;hand trapping&quot;, &quot;low kicks&quot;係相當有<br />\n<br />\n用，都比一d ufc拳手所應用。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想討論現代化中國傳統武術，有冇得搞?<br />\n<br />\n利申番我淨係有睇boxing同少量mma<br />\n對中國武術/詠春極少認識<br />\n希望有專家討論"},{"pid":"b56225e4cddfe7614e8af0319ae98ba625bbc08b","tid":588933,"uid":71568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/222318_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F222318_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=633d7772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/222330_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F222330_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=d747e4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一d李小龍同人spar既gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c57e4b661f846bc816